# Ticket #5 – Group Membership Issue

## Issue:
User cannot access the inventory control shared folder

## Investigation:
Open Active Directory and client computer
Located the user account
Checked the user’s group memberships
Verified the user was missing from the inventory staff security group

## Root Cause:
The user was not assigned to the correct active directory inventory staff group to access inventory resources

## Resolution:
Added the user Lennet Naranjo to the inventory staff security group
Verified the users group membership was updated

## Verification:
User successfully accessed the inventory control shared folder
